---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Throat Song
Description: February 5
---

Let your throat-song
be clear and strong enough

to make an emperor fall full-length,
suppliant, at the door.
